# --- Local dev ---
# In dev, requests to /api are proxied to VITE_API_TARGET (default
# http://localhost:8000) by vite.config.ts. Leave VITE_API_BASE unset locally.
VITE_API_TARGET=http://localhost:8000

# --- Production (Vercel) ---
# Point the frontend at the deployed backend. Set this in the Vercel project's
# Environment Variables (Production + Preview). Use the full Render URL + /api,
# with NO trailing slash, e.g.:
# VITE_API_BASE=https://incidentiq-api.onrender.com/api
